OL,5, The Met has admitted it wrote to more  
OL,6, than 250 retired police officers with  
OL,7, misconduct records inviting them to    
OL,8, re-apply for their former jobs.        
OL,10,FIt has also been revealed that they    
OL,11,Fwrote to a further 99 officers who     
OL,12,Fretired while under investigation.     
OL,14,FThe findings were originally revealed  
OL,15,Fby a Freedom of Information request    
OL,16,Ffrom The Times.                        
OL,18,FThe force has apologised, saying       
OL,19,Fwriting to the officers without due    
OL,20,Fchecks was an error.                   
